main.enactingFormula: Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the United States of America in Congress assembled,

section.heading: Captain Humayun Khan Post Office.
section.content: Section 1(a) of Public Law 115–347 (132 Stat. 5054) is amended by striking “180 McCormick Road” and inserting “2150 Wise Street”.
